29.84	Michael_Wolff_(journalist)	Michael Wolff (journalist)	Michael Wolff (born August 27, 1953) is an American author, essayist, and journalist. He currently writes a regular column for Vanity Fair magazine. His most recent book, The Man Who Owns the News, is a biography of Rupert Murdoch, based on more than 50 hours of interviews with the media mogul., though upon its release it was criticized for providing little insight into its subject .	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8c/Michael_Wolff.jpg/220px-Michael_Wolff.jpg
